  "id": "RAW_669cd820",
  "title": "上线 14 个月，Notion 关掉了自己的 AI 邮件产品",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247524906&idx=1&sn=d2f1ef624da1f34d6632fe35b98cc02d",
  "date": "2026-06-27 10:30:00",
  "author": "Founder Park",
  "siteName": "Founder Park",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a68a0f9b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FUrL1kkHON7LvjOJdicJvBAMnjTM0kCqUJF2iarHgibCQ2ntbAPtS9Ox941oHFgrFzRuR1RhOrw0QWexgxTx9bH3mRqwNncOP9e3mO838Syj94k%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">6 月 26 日，Notion 在 X 上发布了一条公告：将于 9 月 22 日在 Web、桌面端和 iOS 全面关闭 Notion Mail。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">这款 AI 邮箱客户端 2025 年 4 月才正式上线，总生命周期不过 17 个月。Notion 给出的理由很直接，随着 Agent 能力变得更强，越来越多用户将邮件工作流交给 Agent 处理。\"如今，</span><strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">超过一半的 Notion Mail 用户在不打开收件箱的情况下管理邮件。</span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">因此，我们决定全面转向由 Agent 来管理你的收件箱。\"</span></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f9ceb1a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUrL1kkHON7Ifx0SBS6PC4GQ6uyKNeliaS5EUJA01ZCHF00HynlBdxbqQOL8E803ER2OTBYiaGxqicibjwGAGOrkTxalGZ9bzvPj6dZQ8DeI3SpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">AI 邮件一直是近年来最活跃的生产力赛道之一。一方面，围绕「AI + 邮件」的垂类初创公司持续涌现，并获得了规模不小的融资支持。另一方面，从 Gmail、Outlook 等大厂产品到各类通用工具，都在不断强化邮件处理中的 AI 能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">作为估值 110 亿美元的生产力软件独角兽，Notion 此次却干脆利落地终止了这款上线一年多的主要产品，果断 pivot 了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">过去，AI 在邮件系统中的角色通常是增强体验，带来更好的分类、更智能的筛选、更自然的回复建议，本质仍然是在优化原有的邮箱界面。但如果 Agent 已经可以理解、处理并执行邮件任务，那么邮箱作为人类阅读与操作中介的必要性也开始下降。换句话说，邮件的未来可能不是让人用得更好，而是让人根本不用再看。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:sans-serif;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">⬆️</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;clear:both;font-size:16px;font-family:sans-serif;min-height:1em;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">关注 Founder Park，最及时最干货的创业分享</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;margin-top:32px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6em;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;border-style: solid;border-right-width: 0px;border-bottom-width: 0px;border-left-width: 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin: 0px 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);visibility: visible;\">\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 32px;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;margin-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 14px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Founder Park 正在</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 14px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">持续寻找值得被看见的 AI 团队与项目。</span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 32px;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 32px;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n            <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n             <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;\">\n              <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 32px;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;\">\n               <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;\">\n                <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 14px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们将通过「AI 产品市集」、内容报道、社群分发等方式，帮你触达早期用户、获得真实反馈，以及建立关键连接。</span></span></p>\n                <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 14px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果你正在做 AI 相关的事，欢迎和我们聊聊。&nbsp;</span></span>\n                <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.6em;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;pointer-events: initial;width: 124px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=208d3180&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUrL1kkHON7KtwJvXZC7PKR2vfA8algP47mrNiaVxibSsiaAnqSiaEkZ7sTPEoMfANkcfrug4QCVG0icmRIQqBVPvytreVe5VoPcWAFIjqxxSlHkE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n               </div>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n         <hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;transform:scale(1, 0.5);border-right-width:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;border-bottom-width:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin:0px 0px;border-style:solid;border-left-width:0px;\">\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\"><span>01&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span>邮箱曾是 Notion 挑战 Google Workspace 的重要一环</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">Notion Mail 的故事始于 2024 年 Notion 对协作软件公司 Skiff 的收购。Skiff 此前以安全加密为核心卖点，产品包括加密文档协作、邮箱、日历、云盘等。但被收购后不到一年，Skiff 原有的邮件服务便被关闭。基于这支团队，Notion 在 2025 年 4 月正式推出了 Notion Mail，向所有用户开放。</span></span></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=818c68a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUrL1kkHON7LCEUw6uneAQictXFva5HSKYxEMlq8l7gj4A5WUjUBI4cWd1e88mjvpzicEN9Gm6GRsvZH104GEiarmiazOBZHppiaTkRaydnBRHYAs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">除了旗舰应用 Notion 本身，公司的生产力版图中还包括 Notion Calendar 和 Notion Web Clipper。Notion Mail 承载着 Notion 挑战 Microsoft Office 和 Google Workspace 的雄心，要成为用户所有工作的中心枢纽，就必须把邮箱做好。在 Notion 的构想中，Notion Mail 并非普通的 Gmail 客户端，其核心差异在于 AI 的深度嵌入。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">一方面，用户可以通过自然语言提示词实现对邮件的自动整理。比如直接写一句话，「按照招聘流程阶段为所有招聘邮件打标签，并显示对应岗位」，AI 就能自动执行分类，不再需要手动设置复杂的筛选条件。另一方面，Notion 也希望让 AI 接管繁琐的邮件往来，会议安排、后续跟进、重复性沟通等工作，统统都可以交给 AI 处理。</span></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=94db23e9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FUrL1kkHON7K2TcAR4Sz4iap3KFI2Ilic74AG3A9Q4oRg8mnKJ7Q9swKicG9GvsswqMqY01fKxibLP7dZdPZtAn6knPPrEEGUwQn052gh9D5fHUo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">前 Skiff 联创、Notion Mail 团队负责人之一 Andrew Milich 曾表示，他们的愿景是\"重新定义收件箱\"。比起永无止境的邮件列表，收件箱而应该成为一个数据库。用户可以像在 Notion 中一样，对它进行筛选、排序和组织。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight: bold;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\">02</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span>Notion 的取舍：</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span>保留日历，让 Agent 吞掉收件箱</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">Notion Mail 的宏大愿景在一年后便被按下了停止键。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">在官宣关停的推文下，不少 Notion Mail 用户表达了惋惜和不满。其中一名用户写道，「我始终认为需要一个专门的邮件界面。如果能在这个界面中同时配备 Agent，那当然更好，但我不希望只有 Agent。」</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">这代表了当下一种相当现实的需求。即便 Agent 能够处理大部分邮件事务，用户仍然需要一个可见的界面，能够看到全貌、确认细节，在必要的时候手动干预。一个完全消失的收件箱界面，某种程度上也消解了人的「掌控感」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">但 Notion 产品负责人 Max Schoening 给出了不同的判断。他表示，Notion Mail 是团队尝试将「可塑软件」理念带入电子邮件领域的一次探索。但他们越来越相信，软件的未来在于替用户完成工作，而不仅仅是展示工作内容。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">他也坦言了做邮件客户端的现实困难。从功能细节、邮件解析、稳定性到安全性，每一个环节都是漫长的长尾工程。与其在这些地方持续投入，Notion 认为不如把精力集中在邮件的分类、整理和执行上。这是他们从用户行为中观察到需求更为强烈的方向，同时也正在加大对更低成本大模型的投入，强化 AI Agent 在邮件处理中的能力。</span></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2174238a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUrL1kkHON7J3hvibmE6bSczXyAC1vX3CtPDsB2rGpLXw60YC3BH5jHoXkguMnUjibanNVtMvve9tpjtdAy3lPDFCqwbsJlVDSbKLNUmFqeoK4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">一个值得注意的对比是，Notion Calendar 这款 2024 年初上线的日程管理应用并未受影响。Max Schoening 的解释是，时间本质上是一种高度视觉化的信息，天然需要一个界面来呈现。而邮件主要是文本内容，可以自然地存在于聊天线程、数据库等各种形态中，不一定非要有一个专门的收件箱。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">也就是说，在 Notion 的判断里，日历仍然需要 GUI，但邮件可以被 Agent 吞掉。既然看到了这个趋势，Notion 就选择立刻行动，哪怕代价是关停一款上线一年的产品。在快速变化的市场里，及时止损本身就是一种能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight: bold;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\">03</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span>给 Agent 一个独立的邮箱正成为新趋势</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">在 Notion Mail 的关停帖子下，不少 AI 邮箱类产品纷纷「接盘式」发声，希望承接可能流失的用户。但如果仔细看这些公司的产品方向，它们更像是在沿着 Notion 的思路前进，试图打造专门为 AI Agent 服务的邮件系统。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">以创业公司 AgentMail 为例，其联合创始人兼 CEO Haakam Aujla 曾表示，他们从一开始就希望为 AI Agent 提供与 Gmail 类似的邮箱能力，但去掉所有为人类设计的界面元素。「我们希望 Agent 具备搜索、过滤、回复和转发的能力，但它们不应该像人一样点击屏幕上的按钮。对 Agent 来说这太笨重了，它们只需要调用 API 即可。」当然，他们的平台也保留了一个管理界面，供用户查看和管理 Agent 邮箱。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">国内方面，腾讯也在探索类似的方向。6 月 23 日，QQ 邮箱推出了 Agent Mail，定位为\"一款专为 Agent 设计的邮箱\"。它与用户的个人邮箱完全隔离，AI 仅能访问专属邮箱内的内容。同时它不只是一个收件箱，还是 Agent 的独立对外身份，可以自主注册平台、接收验证码，甚至支持企业间 A2A 自动完成询价和订单对接。</span></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5016c01&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUrL1kkHON7IU1cIiaTDwMlibkffMv6KkMiauic49N0FEC17ia53sEeZmvdmvglIHL4czrliahIeT3nRQ7IibHcRLUlK3qfxAaNrTibaZXsuuPtBZMIo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">这背后的逻辑在于，当 Agent 开始替人办事，它需要的不是一个更好的收件箱界面，而是一套独立的通信基础设施，有自己的身份、自己的权限边界、自己的审计记录。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight: bold;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\">04</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span>该考虑给 AI Agent 开发产品了</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">两年前，AI 大多还只是能调用简单工具的聊天机器人。今天，Coding Agent 已经在全球普及，人们开始用 Agent 管理日历、安排会议、搭建营销活动。如果科技行业的判断实现，未来互联网上 AI Agent 的数量甚至可能与真人用户相当。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">在这一趋势下，邮件这个品类正在被重新定义：</span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">对部分用户来说，邮件的未来是\"没有收件箱\"。Agent 直接读取、处理、执行，用户只看结果。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">对 Agent 本身来说，它需要自己的邮件身份和通信能力，而不是借用人类的账号。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">对邮件类创业公司来说，竞争对手可能不再是另一个更好的收件箱，而是\"收件箱\"这个概念本身的消失。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">当然，这不意味着所有人都准备好了把邮件完全交给 AI。邮件涉及沟通、决策、承诺、法律效力，它不像日程安排那样可以容错。在 Agent 的可靠性达到足够高的水平之前，\"没有收件箱\"对大多数人来说仍然是一个过于激进的承诺。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">但深层的转变是，过去的变革方向是 AI Mail，在传统邮件产品上叠加智能能力。而现在出现的新路线是 Mail for AI，直接为 Agent 之间的通信与执行而设计。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\">如果这一逻辑成立，那么\"老产品 + AI\"的思路本身可能只是一个过渡态，真正的方向是给 Agent 造出新工具。邮件如此，日程管理、项目协作、CRM 是否也会走向同样的终局？当 Agent 成为主要的工作执行者，生产力软件或许都将面临同一个问题：你到底是在为人做工具，还是在为 Agent 做工具？</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;\">\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-wrap-style:initial;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:center;\"></div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Notion 宣布关闭上线仅 14 个月的 AI 邮件客户端 Notion Mail，转向由 Agent 完全管理收件箱，这一决策折射出 AI 邮件赛道的根本转变：从优化用户体验的功能叠加，转向为 AI Agent 打造独立通信基础设施。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Notion 宣布关闭上线仅 14 个月的 AI 邮件客户端 Notion Mail，转向由 Agent 完全管理收件箱，这一决策折射出 AI 邮件赛道的根本转变：从优化用户体验的功能叠加，转向为 AI Agent 打造独立通信基础设施。",
  "summary": "本文报道了 Notion 将于 2026 年 9 月 22 日全面关闭 Notion Mail 的消息，这款产品从上线到关停仅 17 个月。文章梳理了 Notion Mail 的诞生背景——源于对 Skiff 的收购，旨在挑战 Google Workspace，核心是深度嵌入 AI 能力（自然语言标签、自动处理邮件等）。关停的直接原因是超过一半用户已通过 Agent 管理邮件而不再打开收件箱。文章引用了产品负责人的表态，分析 Notion 的取舍逻辑：日历因高度视觉化需要 GUI，而邮件本质是文本，可以被 Agent 处理，因此保留日历、放弃邮件客户端。同时，文章观察到「Mail for AI」的新趋势——专为 Agent 设计的邮箱（如 AgentMail、QQ 邮箱 Agent Mail），Agent 拥有独立身份和通信能力，而不再需要人类界面。最后提出深层问题：当 Agent 成为主要执行者，生产力软件该为人还是为 Agent 设计？文章立场清晰，既有事实报道又有独立判断，对 AI 产品趋势有启发价值。",
